		"description": "<p><em>Prerequisite: Strength 13 or higher </em></p><p>You've developed the skills necessary to hold your own in close-quarters grappling.</p><p>You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>You have advantage on attack rolls against a creature you are grappling.</li><li>You can use your action to try to pin a creature grappled by you. To do so, make another grapple check. If you succeed, you and the creature are both restrained until the grapple ends.</li></ul>",
